644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27468,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/08\/ali-knowledge-narrate-understand\/","url_meta":{"origin":26805,"position":3},"title":"Ali on Hadith: Narrate to people only what they can understand","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Tufayl reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cSpeak to people only according to their level of knowledge. Would you like for Allah and His Messenger to be denied?\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 127 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0637\u064f\u0651\u0641\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0644\u0650 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0623\u0645\u064a\u0631\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7672,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/05\/dua-prophet-rain-miracle\/","url_meta":{"origin":26805,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Miracles: The Prophet prays for rain, it rains","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, on Friday while he was delivering a sermon in Medina. The man said, \u201cThere is no rain, so please call upon your Lord to bless us with rain.\u201d The Prophet looked at the sky\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36744,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/08\/01\/dead-among-living\/","url_meta":{"origin":26805,"position":5},"title":"Hudhayfah on Fitnah: Who are the dead among the living?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Tufayl reported: It was said to Hudhayfah, may Allah be pleased with him, \u201cWho are the dead among the living?\u201d Hudhayfah said, \u201cThose who do not recognize good in their hearts and do not reject evil in their hearts.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 37577 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0651\u064f\u0641\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0644\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26805","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=26805"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26805\/revisions"}],"wp:attachmen